description: Simple design, maximum performance and a minimum price were the blueprints used to develop the EXM2500S. Loaded with 210lbs. of cast iron resistance, the EXM2500S can perform your most demanding strength training routines. Muscular growth and definition are rapidly achieved throughout each of the precision built, biomechanically designed stations. Includes the 2:1 ratio Leg Press station, which converts the 210 lb. weight stack into 420 lbs. of resistance!
features: 6 UNIQUE WORKOUT STATIONS: Multi-Press Station Lat Pulldown/High Pulley, Ab Crunch/Mid Pulley, Leg Extension/Leg Curl, Leg Press, Seated Row/Low Pulley which features a 210lbs. stack with state of the art nylon bushings for smooth and quiet operation.

INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

INCLUDED ATTACHMENTS: Fully adjustable single-stack home gym workout machine featuring a no-cable change design lat pull down bar, low row bar, leg press bar, ab harness comfortable multi-position handgrips and adjustable hold-down pads to target several muscle groups (abs, biceps calves, delts forearms, glutes hamstrings, lats lower back, obliques pectorals, quads shoulders traps, tricepts and total body).

EXERCISES: Use this home gym to complete a variety of full body workouts (pec fly, bench, incline, standing military and decline press, pull over, crossover, upright row wide and close grip front lat pulldowns and pull up, ab crunch, back extension bicep and leg curls, tricep press down and kickback, leg extension, glute kick.
DIMENSIONS: Heavy-duty construction with 2" x 4" 12 gauge high tensile strength steel frame and sealed bearings. Measures 89"x79"x83". Lifetime manufacutrer warranty.

title: CREWORKS Electric Wire Stripper Machine, 0.06"-1" Automatic Wire Stripping Machine, Wire Stripping Tool for 1.5-25 mm Scrap Wire, 5 Channel Copper Wire Stripper Power Tool for Leftover Cable Recycling
breadCrumbs: Tools & Home Improvement › Power & Hand Tools › Hand Tools › Strippers › Wire Strippers
features: Wire Stripping Made Easy: The Creworks electric wire stripper removes insulation from old electrical wiring with speeds up to 98 ft./min. (30 m/min.), powering its durable steel blade with an efficient 180W motor
Big or Small, We Strip It All: The 5 separate feed holes on this automatic cable stripper cover wires from 0.06" to 1" (1.5 to 25 mm), letting you safely and easily handle the most common wire sizes

Effortless & Safe: Set the blade height to suit your exact needs using the adjustment knob, hit the power button, and start feeding your copper cable through the appropriate hole. The emergency stop is standing by if anything goes awry
Clean Cut Every Time: This wire stripping tool's alloy steel blade maintains its sharp edge for clean cuts with each use. The reinforced aluminum frame ensures dependable & long-lasting use

Portable on the Go: This electric cable stripping machine is small and easy to carry. Take it from your home to shed, workshop, or worksite, and turn your scrap wires into valuable treasure wherever needed

Product Description
MOST EFFECTIVE ANKLE STRAP PAIR FOR LEG AND GLUTE WORKOUTS 
For shapely legs and a firmer butt, working your glutes is key. Designed especially for kickback exercises, our resistance band ankle straps are made for a more comfortable, and in turn, more effective workout. That means that every time you hit the gym, you’ll be getting the maximum benefit from your workout. Turn it up, feel the burn, and build the booty you’ve always dreamed about! 
Get the most out of every gym visit and work your way to a body that looks great. Whether you’re at the beach, out with the girls, or down at the gym, everyone will envy your slim figure and tight butt! Tone and trim your muscles to build a flawless physique and feel confident about how you look. 
VERSATILE AND MULTIPURPOSE 
An essential gym accessory, our gym ankle strap for cable machine can be used with cable machines, resistance trainers, and other gym equipment. If you’re exercising at home, they’re perfect for adding intensity and support to glute kickbacks, leg extensions, and weight training. 
Use them to warm up your glutes by doing glute kickbacks and side leg raises on the cable machine.Or isolate your quads and hamstrings by doing leg extensions and hamstring curls! 
With these wrist wraps, you’ll instantly realize just what you’ve been missing. 
Our ankle straps are made for you. 
We Are Confident You Will Love Your Ankle Workout Straps! 
What are you waiting for? Start working out now. 
NEOPRENE PADDING, COMFORTABLE WITH ZERO CHAFING 
The lining adds comfort and softness neoprene so that more gently adhere to the skin. 7mm thickness ensures that the force is evenly distributed when you perform each movement. You’ll come away from your workout with no ankle pain whatsoever. 
Our cable machine ankle attachment don’t fray, break, or lose their shape. The velcro is thick, sticks down securely, and is built to last. You can use them for years - our velcro will hold up and keep you on track for a better body and firmer butt. 
FOR A CANFIDENT SAFE WORKOUT 
When you workout, you need to be confident your gear will do the job. Other ankle straps slip, slide, and ride up the leg. That means you’ll constantly need to interrupt your exercise and readjust them. 
HPYGN cable leg attachments for gym are different. Our unique, cleverly designed kickback straps hold the main strap firmly in place, stopping it from sliding up your leg. That means that even if you’re pulling a heavy weight, your straps will grip onto your ankles and never let go - without shifting or chafing. No matter how hard you work out, you can be confident the cable ankle attachments for gym will hold up.

The fully functional professional carriage system utilizes four high resin pulleys on each side with patented nylon bushing technology and eight sealed ball bearings for smooth, continuous movement during your cable workout. The top and bottom pulleys swivel smoothly with more than 180-degrees of motion for frictionless training in all directions. This cable cross machine accepts both Olympic and standard plates (each sold separately) and comes with two cable handles and one ankle strap. When assembled, the Powerline Cable Crossover Machine measures 112 by 39 by 82 inches (L x W x H) and weighs 133 pounds. It is backed by the Powerline 10-Year In-Home , which covers the frame for 10 years and all other parts for one year. Add the Lat Pull-Up/Chin-Up Station (GCA2) to add even more versatility (sold separately).Amazon.comThe Cable Crossover Machine from Powerline offers smooth and friction-free 180-degree motion that allows you to exercise virtually every major muscle group in your body. The system features a wide and tall mainframe with a sturdy build, that provides access to a variety of high and low pulley exercises. The professional carriage system utilizes patented nylon bushing technology and eight sealed ball bearing with large-diameter high resin pulleys to guarantee smooth operation. The top and bottom pulleys swivel with over 180 degrees of movement for frictionless guidance in all directions. The system includes the mainframe as well as two cable handles and one ankle strap. Chin-up handles, standard and Olympic weight plates, and collars can be used with this system but are sold separately.Features and Specifications:Professional carriage system Professional carriage system Patented nylon bushing technology Patented nylon bushing technology Eight sealed ball bearing Eight sealed ball bearing High resin pulleys High resin pulleys Top and bottom pulleys offer over 180 degrees of movement Top and bottom pulleys offer over 180 degrees of movement Accepts both Olympic and standard plates Accepts both Olympic and standard plates Chin-up handles, weight plates, and collars optional (sold separately) Chin-up handles, weight plates, and collars optional (sold separately) Assembled dimensions: 82 by 112 by 39 inches (H x L x W) Assembled dimensions: 82 by 112 by 39 inches (H x L x W)
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

SUPERIOR QUALITY: The Body-Solid Cable Crossover machine is a testament to our commitment to quality and reliability. It is a top-tier gym equipment, designed with an industry-leading technology that features a patented nylon bushing technology and eight sealed ball bearing, high resin pulleys. This cable machine is not just a piece of equipment, it's an investment in your health and fitness goals.

VERSATILITY: The Body-Solid Cable Crossover machine offers total body exercise with an endless array of high and low pulley exercises. The top and bottom pulleys swivel smoothly and fully with over 180° of movement, allowing for frictionless guidance in all directions.

EXERCISES: Use this home gym to complete a variety of full body workouts (pec fly, bench, incline, crossover, upright row, deltoid raise, shoulder press, close grip front lat pullup and pulldown, bent over row, seated row, ab crunch, oblique bend, tricep press down, outer and inner thigh abduction, calf press, reverse fly, glute kickback and many more.

DIMENSIONS: This CABLE CROSSOVER is a dynamic addition to any home gym and garage gym exercise program. Measures 37"x113"x83" and weighs 102lbs. 10 year manufacutrer warranty on frame, and 1 year on parts.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
FOR A CONFIDENT AND SAFE WORKOUT 
When you workout, you need to be confident your gear will do the job. Other ankle straps slip, slide, and ride up the leg. That means you’ll constantly need to interrupt your exercise and readjust them. 
Our unique, cleverly designed kickback straps hold the main strap firmly in place, stopping it from sliding up your leg. That means that even if you’re pulling a heavy weight, your straps will grip onto your ankles and never let go. 
Made from comfortable, breathable fabric that's soft and lightweight to keep you comfortable during your workouts.
We are committed to providing our customers with the best shopping experience, and if you have any questions, we will do our best to support you.

description: Body-Solid takes state-of-the-art crossover stations to new heights with the Deluxe Cable Crossover, a dynamic addition to any home gym exercise program. Sturdy and stable, the new design lets you exercise virtually every major muscle group in your body. Interchangeable cable handles provide an unlimited number of possibilities for all experience levels, and the extra wide and tall mainframe provides you with easy access to an endless array of high and low pulley exercises. The Deluxe Cable Crossover's unique pull-up station offers multiple grip positions, and dual independent carriages have been ergonomically designed to offer twice as many height adjustments as previous Body-Solid crossover stations. With 20 independent height adjustments and 180° cable positioning for frictionless guidance in all directions, the Body-Solid GDCC250 is one of the most versatile and functional machines manufactured today. When it's time to extend yourself and stretch the limits of your optimum workout, the GDCC250 Deluxe Cable Center will be pulling for you to achieve your goals.
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body-Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

EXERCISES: Use this home gym to complete a variety of full body workouts (pec fly, bench, incline, crossover, upright row, deltoid raise, shoulder press, close grip front lat pullup and pulldown, bent over row, seated row, ab crunch, oblique bend, tricep press down, outer and inner thigh abduction, calf press, reverse fly, glute kickback and many more.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Portable Cable Machine 
The PT1 enables you to do any workout that you could do on a full sized cable machine while only needing a fraction of the space. 
Requires little to no set up ✓ Use anywhere indoors & outdoors ✓ Perfect size for traveling ✓ Convenient storage ✓ Simple and effective ✓ Great for rehab & injury prevention ✓ 
Features 
Versatile 
The PT1 Complete Package includes object attachments, a wall mount, an ankle strap, and workout handle, allowing for greater variety of workouts and locations. Simply strap the object attachment to anything sturdy or mount the Pulle with a wall mount in a dedicated fitness area. Find variety in your training by using the snap hooks to swap out any of the attachments! 
Adjustable 
The Pulle PT1 can be set at three adjustable levels of resistance up to 16.5 lbs, it is low-impact and great for any type of training. Whether you need to build strength after an injury, warm-up for sports, or get a full body workout, the Pulle PT1 is made for all training levels. 
Portable 
The Pulle also has a quality drawstring bag to bring it along anywhere you go! The Pulle can easily replace multiple resistance bands or the multiple sets of dumbbells. This is a SAFER option to carrying weights or potentially snapping a resistance band! 
Double the Resistance - Double the Workouts 
Get TWO Pulle PT1s to double the resistance of your workouts or use both sides of your body at the same time. Two Pulle's allows for a greater variety of movements, a heavier resistance for strength training, and quicker workouts while being able to target both sides of your body at the same time. 
Doctor Recommended 
"As a movement professional I would highly recommend this product. I have always loved being active. Growing up I played soccer, basketball, track and cross-country. When I tore my ACL and meniscus, I experienced physical therapy first hand and also discovered a career path. Now as a physical therapist, I get to know my patients and encourage movement in a safe and functional way."

features: Commercial Grade for Home Gym & Garage Gym Use: Strong hamstrings and quadriceps are crucial for balance, speed and coordination. You'll wish every day was leg day with LIONSCOOL Leg Machine. Unique cable and pulley system supplies consistent resistance throughout the motions, which differs from traditional lever operated machine and assists with the growth of stronger and more defined muscles. It can be used for seated leg extension and lying leg curl. Only seated leg curl is not applicable.

Excel in Your Toughest Workouts with the Ultra-Robust Structure: The upgraded hinge jointed lifting arm, combined with a strong pulley and reinforced 8mm-thick cable, allows for a plate loading capacity of up to 600LBS and will last through grueling workouts. The whole machine is constructed with 14-gauge tube and purpose built on a creative rectangular base with enlarged stepped plate feet to distribute pressure and eliminate rocking, ensuring an outstanding 1000LBS user capacity.

Experience Exercise with Smooth Pulley System: Our Innovative pulley system delivers consistent resistance tailored to the specific strength curve of the targeted muscle group. We specially design an adjustable bolt to regulate tension in case the cable stretches out over the years. You will find pleasure in the seamless resistance during your workout. Plate loading post measures 12” and fits 2-inch weight plates smoothly with its hard chrome plated surface.

Extreme Easy, Convenient Access & Adjustment: We discard the impractical knee holder to make getting in and off the machine effortless and smooth. 6 seat depth adjustable backrest will accommodate users of all heights. Our self-adjusting foot roller with its 7 angles adjustable arm will conform to your leg position freely and the seat is quickly adjustable by one pull pin between seated and prone positions.

Creative Seat Structure and Feel Comfort in Details: We have unique three-segment seat structure to maximize your comfort during your lying leg curls. The seat pad, middle pad and the backrest as well as the foam foot roller, are all 2.2” thick with high density EPE foam, combining firm support with gentle feel. All cushions feature textured PU surface to ensure anti-slip performance. And two pairs of rubber grip ergonomic handles located on both sides help assist body stability.

Awesome Addition to Home Gym with Reliable Warranty: It can fit into your home gym like a workout bench with assembled upright dimension 45” width x 56” depth x 41” height and laid down depth 67”. We offer Manufacturer Limited Warranty: 2 years on framework (structural steel & welds) and 1 year on other parts. Assembly instructions and wrenches are included. It is surely a cost-effective investment of your fitness equipment. Please note it comes in two packages and may arrive separately.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Why Did We Design This Power Rack? 
Traditional Power Cages come with certain limitations. They often fall short in targeting specific muscle groups, such as the chest line. To address these challenges, we re-designed the whole cable system to train full body more convenient and easier. 
With this gym monster, you can do Squat, Bench Press, Lat Pull-down, Low Row Exercise, Cable Crossover Exercise, Landmine Press, Battle Rope Exercise etc.. 
Previous page
Next page
A costly power rack may be out of reach, but a low quality budget option isn't the solution either. What people truely need is a durable, reliable and built-to-last power rack. With this in mind, we designed this well-built power rack under $500. QUALITY AND SAFETY ALWAYS COME FIRST. 
Assembled Size 	46.5″ Width x 59″ Depth x 85.4″ Height 	
Product Weight 	206LBS 	
Foot Print 	46.5" x 59". Comfortable for gym lover from small to large body sizes 	
Minimum Ceiling Height 	85.4". The recommend minimum ceiling height (to be able to do a full pull-up) is about 96" 	
Hole Choice 	15 holes on uprights. Suitable for people of different heights to perform squats and bench presses 	
Hole Size 	1 inch diameter. Compatible with most of power cage attachments 	
Installation 	Easy installation Design. We recommend you use 17mm wrench and socket set to assemble this gym monster 	
Shipping 	Two packages will be shipped separately. Two tracking numbers will be sent to you via Email 	
Package 	Add plywood to the inner layer of the 5A-grade corrugated cardboard box to maximize protection against rough handling during transit 	
Attachments 	3 Handle Bar (Lat pulldown Bar, Short Bar, T Bar), 2 Sport Arms, 2 J-hooks, 2 Dip Bars, 1 Landmine, 1 Foot Board, 1 Battle Rope Ring and 4 Band Pegs 	
Front Uprights 	2" x 2" galvanized steel. More durable, maintaining a like-new shine even after long-term pulley adjustments 	
Back Uprights 	2" x 2" power-coated steel 	
Pulley System Style 	2 electroplated round tubes instead of one square tube. No frequently jams, luxury cable exercise experience 	
Pulley System Ratio 	2:1 	
Quick Pulley Adjustment 	1 second adjustment. Better spring plug, better galvanized uprights, better ball bearing pulley wheels 	
Cable Cover 	High-wear-resistant TPU material. It remains tear-free after long-term use 	
We upgraded finish, using electroplated steel for the front uprights, ensuring they stay sleek and shiny even after long-term use. We want this power rack to remain a showpiece in your home gym for years to come. When your friend walks in your home gym, and their reaction is a genuine “Wow!”

With multiple training modes, including Standard, Eccentric, and Isokinetic, Elastic, and Rowing, this device caters to various exercise preferences. Its wireless BT streaming capability ensures a seamless connection to your devices. Crafted with heavy-duty, high-quality materials, it can endure high-strength stretching exercises and prevent injuries, making it suitable for weight training, bodybuilding, and various sports. Get resistance of up to 75lbs on each side, totalling 150 lbs. of total resistance. The ergonomic design allows you to target different muscle groups, including legs, back, and arms. Its compact dimensions make it easily portable, ensuring you can stay on top of your workout game wherever you go. Elevate your fitness journey with the Travel Multifunctional Apollo Board Device – your ultimate fitness companion.

What is the minimum ceiling height I need? 
Machine height is 87.2'', the minimum ceiling height to be able to do a full pull up with your head above the pull-up bar is 102''. 
Does the M4 take up a lot of space? 
No, it just takes up only 23.64 square feet of space. 
What is the pulley ratio? 
The pulley ratio is 2:1, meaning if you have 100 pounds loaded, the resistance is 50 pounds. M4 is equipped with dual independent cable systems. Loading capacity of cable system: 400 Pounds on each side. 
How to bench press heavy without a spotter? 
M4 comes with 6mm thick safety catches and safety stoppers, and 10 height adjustments. Set the safety stoppers just above chest height as the barbell is lowered. If you fail, the stopper will catch the bar, preventing it from crushing you. 
Does it come with weights, bench, or a barbell? 
No, they are all available in M4 Home Gym Package.

Instructions for Adjusting the Cable Machine 
Loosen the Popper Pin: Turn the popper pin counterclockwise to loosen it.
Pull Out the Popper Pin: Gently pull the popper pin outward to release the locking mechanism.
Move the Sleeve to the Desired Height: Slide the sleeve along the guide rail to the preferred height for your exercise.
Push the Popper Pin Back into the Hole: Align the sleeve with the hole for the desired height and push the popper pin back in until it clicks securely into place.
Tighten the Popper Pin: Turn the popper pin clockwise to secure it firmly and lock the sleeve in position.
Your cable machine is now ready for use. Adjust the sleeve as needed to target specific muscle groups effectively and safely.

Product Description
Mikolo 5th Generation Home Gym Station Is Coming!!! 
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
[9-IN-1 GYM STATION] Combines a Power Cage, Functional Trainer, Lat Pulldown, Low Row, Smith Machine, Chin Up, Dip Station, Core Trainer, and Suspension Trainer. [3-IN-1 STORAGE SYSTEM] Combines 6 weight storage pins, 4 handle storage hooks, and 2 barbell holders.

What is the minimum ceiling height I need? 
Machine height is 87.2'', the minimum ceiling height to be able to do a full pull up with your head above the pull-up bar is 102''. 
Does the M4 take up a lot of space? 
No, it just takes up only 23.64 square feet of space. 
What is the pulley ratio? 
The pulley ratio is 2:1, meaning if you have 100 pounds loaded, the resistance is 50 pounds. M4 is equipped with dual independent cable systems. Loading capacity of cable system: 400 Pounds on each side. 
How to bench press heavy without a spotter? 
M4 comes with 6mm thick safety catches and safety stoppers, and 10 height adjustments. Set the safety stoppers just above chest height as the barbell is lowered. If you fail, the stopper will catch the bar, preventing it from crushing you.

title: StripMeister Original Drill-Powered Wire Stripper Machine - Manual Wire Stripping Made Easy, Copper Wire Stripper, Drill Wire Stripper, Electric Wire Stripping & Stripping Tool Drill Attachment
breadCrumbs: Tools & Home Improvement › Power & Hand Tools › Hand Tools › Strippers › Wire Strippers
features: ULTRA-GRIP WIRE STRIPPER TECHNOLOGY: Our stripping machine improved with ultra-grip wire feeder technology. This technology massively increases torque, reduces slippage and straightens mangled wires to get them through the drill-powered wire stripper tool. It will untangle mangled wires effortlessly without any slips or jams. This unique cable stripper is an industrial grade automatic wire stripper for all your scrap wire.

PORTABLE WIRE STRIPPER: You can bring this wire stripper machine where all the scrap wires and cables need to be stripped. The tool is lightweight, portable, and can easily fit in a bag or at the back of your truck or car for easy transport and storage. This wire stripping machine won't require a lot of space to strip all the copper wire you have. This drill-powered wire stripping machine is manufactured in North America and uses top-grade materials.

DRILL-POWERED WIRE STRIPPING: Got a hand drill at home? Pair it with the StripMeister original wire stripping machine, and you've got a powerful tool that can handle various types of wires, from 18 gauge to 250 MCM, including braided (stranded) wire. This wire stripper is your partner for practical and economical wire recycling.

VERSATILE WIRE STRIPPER TOOL: Our drill-powered wire stripping tool can handle wire scraps of different sizes, from #18 to 250 MCM, with diameters ranging from 0.08″ (2mm) to 0.79″ (20.1mm). This wire stripping tool can also easily strip braided (stranded) wires. Many copper wire recyclers trust this stripper tool. The specialized slot will save 33% of your time compared to other wire insulation stripping tools.

EFFICIENT SCRAP WIRE STRIPPING: This powerful wire stripping machine can handle kinked and twisted cables and wires. You can go through scraps all day faster than you would with manual hand crank wire stripping. No need to tire yourself out, either, because you can reduce your time stripping copper wires with this product.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Effortlessly strip pinched, kinked, damaged, and pig-tail spiraled copper wires on the first pass without slippage or jams with the StripMeister Original wire stripping machines. Our drill-powered wire stripper machine is constructed from solid aircraft-grade aluminum alloy, with the drive shaft crafted from heavy-duty steel. Blades and feeders are precision-machined with 5-axis CNC milling technology using heat-treated tool steel for optimum quality, durability, and performance. 
Reduce your stripping time with StripMeister Original. The wire reference indicator feature from our drill-powered wire stripper reduces setup time between different gauges of copper wires. With a powerful Ultra-Grip wire feeder that cuts through kinked and twisted wires and cables, you’ll be able to strip wires faster than ever before. Our compact, reliable wire stripping machine makes it possible for you to strip meters of tangled wires effortlessly and have the option to easily fit them in a bag or at the back of your truck or car for easy transport and storage. 
Whether you are a professional electrician or an enthusiast scrap metal recycler looking for a reliable, hassle-free copper wire stripping machine, our StripMeister Original wire stripper machine is the perfect match for your needs. This innovative wire stripping machine features a new contoured copper wire feeding guide that eliminates wire jams while increasing torque and reducing slippage. StripMeister Original can also untangle braided and stranded wires and cables.

CONVENIENT PLATE HOLDERS: This cable crossover machine can accommodate several different weight plates because it has 4 bumper holders. The plate holders measure 9.75” each. BUILD YOUR MUSCLE: If you’re hoping for effective muscle growth, then our cable crossover machine is for you. aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Check it out! The Panther is the ultimate destination for your home gym journey 
The video showcases the product in use.The video guides you through product setup.The video compares multiple products.The video shows the product being unpacked.
Does this machine come with all the bells and whistles, or do I have to buy extra stuff? 
Oh, it’s got all the bells and whistles, my friend. No need to go hunting for extra gear. You’ve got your Smith machine, pec deck, cable pulley system, pull-up bars... it’s a one-stop shop for your entire workout. Just bring your muscles. 
What’s with the 7-degree angled Smith machine? Does that actually make a difference? 
Oh yeah, big time! That 7-degree angle isn’t just for looks—it’s all about smoother, more natural movement. No more “joint grinds” that feel like you’re wrestling with the machine. You’ll feel like you're lifting with the pros. 
Can I actually fit this beast in my garage, or is it gonna need its own room? 
It’s a powerhouse, but we designed it to save space. Think of it like a Transformer—big performance, compact design. It'll fit in your garage or home gym without turning it into a circus tent. 
What’s the deal with the cable ratios? 
No calculators needed! Here's the breakdown: 
4:1 on the pulley system 
2:1 on the pec deck 
1:1 on the low row 
Mix these ratios, and you’ve got versatile training for every muscle, every angle. It’s like having a whole gym in one machine! 
Is the pec deck on this machine really as good as it sounds, or is it just a gimmick? 
Nope, no gimmicks here! The built-in pec deck is smooth, comfy, and hits your chest just right. Adjustable settings let you customize for the perfect stretch and contraction. It's like having a trainer, minus the sweat!

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
ORANGE FOREST Ankle Strap for Cable Machine 
Why choose the ORANGE FOREST Ankle Strap for your workout? 
Upgraded 4-D loop ankle strap for women and men, the ankle strap is padded with comfortable 7mm thick, 4" wide neoprene that is very soft for added comfort. Designed to fit the human foot structure for greater comfort and flexibility, it fits all types of legs and feet. The ankle strap is designed with a sturdy Velcro strap that is lightweight and easy to adjust. Super easy to put on and take off. 
Neoprene liner for great comfort 
The liner adds comfort and softness to the neoprene for gentler adhesion to the skin. 7mm thickness ensures even distribution of forces as you perform each movement. 
4 D-ring design 
Each ankle exercise band is designed with 4 D-rings. The double-loop design allows for more even weight distribution and does not strain the muscles, making the exercise safer and more effective. And you can quickly connect the cable machine in seconds. 
Sturdy nylon webbing and reinforced stitching 
Ensure long-lasting equipment strength, which allows you to easily perform your workout without injury or any discomfort. 
Easy adjustment 
The adjustable Velcro design is easy for you to put on and take off. It can fit all sizes of feet. One size fits all 
How to use in the gym? 
Combine with the gym's pulling machine and adjust the weight of the pulling machine to fully and effectively exercise your gluteus maximus, gluteus medius and gluteus minimus muscles to achieve peach butt. 
How to use at home? 
You can use it for light weight and frequency training by pairing it with resistance bands or kickback cables.

How is the Power Rack packaged? 
The machine comes in 3 boxes. 
What is the delivery timeframe for the Power Rack? 
We use FedEx Ground for delivery, and it typically takes 5-10 days for the package to arrive. 
Does this machine require self-assembly? 
Yes. Due to the heavy weight of the machine, you might need an extra pair of hands to help with the assembly. However, the process is straightforward, and you can easily follow our instruction manual or assembly video to set it up. 
How should I tighten bolts and nuts during assembly? 
Hand-tighten bolts and nuts during assembly to allow for adjustments as needed. Once the entire unit is assembled, securely tighten all hardware. 
What maintenance is required for bolts and screws? 
Periodically check for loose bolts and screws, especially after initial use. Tighten them if necessary to ensure the unit remains safe and stable.

description: Define the motions that are right for you and your individual workout goals with the Body-Solid GDCC200 Functional Training Center. This dual independent weight stack system provides dedicated resistance with true iso lateral movements. Core stability training can lead to improved balance, coordination, and stability. By efficiently working your body's stabilizer muscles though a limitless number of exercises, the GDCC200 Functional Training Center offers strength-building results to users of all sizes. Unrestricted multiple planes of motion approximate the muscle activity required for many of the activities you do in everyday life. The Body-Solid GDCC200 features ergonomically designed adjustments and interchangeable cable handles engineered to put hundreds of strength-building exercises within your grasp. With a space-saving footprint, dual independent weight stacks, user-friendly ergonomics and adjustability and precision-fitted components, the GDCC200 Functional Training Center isolates an unbeatable value in today's advanced fitness market. From cable crossovers and shoulder presses to pull-ups, leg kickbacks and everything in between, make a motion to improve your core, build your strength and increase your endurance with the Body-Solid GDCC200.
features: INDUSTRY LEADER: For 30+ years, Body-Solid has held the widest array of products designed to meet the demands of the ever-changing fitness industry (home gym, free weight machines, treadmills, bikes, ellipticals, weight plates, kettlebells, dumbbells, flooring, accessories and more). Our products are cutting edge and reliable and are built for Life……Your Life.

VERSATILE & CUSTOMIZABLE: This dual independent weight stack system provides dedicated resistance with true isolateral movements. From cable crossovers and shoulder presses to pull-ups, leg kickbacks and everything in between, make a motion to improve your core, build your strength and increase your endurance with this exercise machine.

STURDY CONSTRUCTION: This cable crossover machine has a sturdy construction and an extra-wide mainframe provides users with a high-quality machine that is both cost-effective and budget-friendly. This machine allows users to access a near-unlimited number of high and low pulley exercises while working every major muscle group. Includes two 160 lb. weight stacks (weight ratio is 1/2 : 1).

EXERCISES: Use this home gym to complete a variety of full body workouts (pec fly, bench, incline, crossover, upright row, deltoid raise, shoulder press, close grip front lat pullup and pulldown, bent over row, seated row, ab crunch, oblique bend, tricep press down, outer and inner thigh abduction, calf press, reverse fly, glute kickback and many more.

DIMENSIONS: Heavy-duty construction with 11-gauge, 2" x 4" oval tubing with an electrostatically applied powder coat finish. Measures 43"x 73"x 84" and weighs 514lbs. This product is Commercial Rated and features a Lifetime Warranty on frames, welds, weight plates & guide rods. 3 Years on pulleys, bushing, bearings & hardware. 1 Year on cables, upholstery, grips and all other components.

title: Marcy Pro Deluxe Smith Cage Home Gym System for Weight Training SM-7553
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Racks & Cages › Smith Machines
description: The Marcy Pro Deluxe Smith Cage Home Gym System – SM-7553 is an all-in-one home gym cage. This sturdy Smith Home Gym has an incredible number of features suited for beginners and advanced users alike. The SM-7553 is an all-in-one smith cage because it offers a plethora of features only found in club gyms, such as a smith machine and cable crossovers. In addition, the multi-grip pull up bar and detachable dip bars deliver body weight workouts without the need of a separate power tower.Use the included bar catch / safety catches for presses, squats and more. Complete leg presses using the leg press attachment and use the landmine attachment for several different landmine workouts including landmine squats, landmine rows, and more. Purchase resistance bands / tubes separately to use with the included anchor rods to add a different form of resistance to your workout, such as assisted or weighted pullup/dip exercises. The following included accessories ensure you can complete almost every exercise you can think of with the Marcy Deluxe Smith Cage Home Gym System – Lat Bar, Short Bar, Ankle Strap, V-Bar, V-Handle, triceps rope, and barbell pad.The included adjustable bench has a saw-tooth adjustment for the back pad so you can quickly and securely switch between incline, flat, and decline positions. For your comfort, the seat pad portion also has 4 different adjustment angles. For your convenience, the transport wheels make it easy to move the bench around as necessary for your workouts. Finally, the preacher curl pad and leg developer are detachable to make space for different workouts.
features: DELUXE SMITH CAGE - The Marcy Pro Deluxe Smith Cage Home Gym System is a smith machine and power rack in one. Use the ultra-smooth chrome smith machine to safely workout on your own. And use the included bar catch / safety catches to complete squats, presses, and more.

ALL-IN-ONE HOME GYM - The SM-7553 Deluxe Smith Cage Home Gym also includes traditional power tower features. Use the adjustable dip station for dips, or the multi-grip pull up station for pull-ups, chin-ups, and more. The row plate on the SM-7553 helps provide grip for your seated rows.

MULTIPLE EXERCISE OPTIONS - The SM-7553 offers a wide variety attachment for more workouts. Attach the landmine station for landmine squats and leg press attachment for leg presses. The resistance band / tube anchor rods can add even more resistance to your workouts as well (resistance bands / tubes not included).

BENCH VERSATILITY - To add to the convenience of this all-in-one smith machine home gym, transport wheels on the bench make it easy to move the bench in between workouts. The arm curl pad and leg developer stations on the bench are detachable to maximize your space during workouts.

BUILT-IN STORAGE - With so much included, the SM-7553 provides storage space so you don’t develop clutter. There are weight plate storage slots for your plates, two barbell storage posts, and storage hooks for some of your included accessories.

From the manufacturer
Marcy Pro Deluxe Smith Cage Machine SM-7553 
Smith Machine and Power Rack in One 
The Marcy Pro Deluxe Smith Cage Home Gym System is a smith machine and power rack in one. Use the ultra-smooth chrome smith machine to safely workout on your own. And use the included bar catch / safety catches to complete squats, presses, and more. 
Adjustable Cable Crossovers 
There are 40 adjustments possible for the cable crossovers on the SM-7553 so you can set them to your ideal position. The cable crossovers are connected to two independent weight trolley systems. As a result, each side of the cable crossover can be used with different weight or allow you to properly even out your exercises. 
Power Tower Features in your All-in-One Home Gym 
The SM-7553 Deluxe Smith Cage Home Gym also includes traditional power tower features. Use the adjustable dip station for dips, or the multi-grip pull up station for pull-ups, chin-ups, and more. The row plate on the SM-7553 helps provide grip for your seated rows. 
Attachments to Increase your Exercise Options 
The SM-7553 offers a wide variety attachment for more workouts. Attach the landmine station for landmine squats and leg press attachment for leg presses. The resistance band / tube anchor rods can add even more resistance to your workouts as well (resistance bands / tubes not included). 
Accessories to take your Workout to the Next Level 
Included with the SM-7553 are a lat bar, short bar, ankle strap, v-bar, v handle, triceps rope, and barbell pad. 
The most Versatile Smith Cage Machine from Marcy Pro 
All the accessories help to make the SM-7553 Deluxe Smith Cage Machine the most well-rounded smith machine by Marcy to date. 
Adjustable Weight Bench Included 
The saw tooth adjustment style on weight bench back pad ensure safe adjustment to the inline, flat, and decline positions. The bench back has 7 angles and the bench seat pad has 4 adjustment angles for your comfort. 
Bench Versatility 
To add to the convenience of this all-in-one smith machine home gym, transport wheels on the bench make it easy to move the bench in between workouts. The arm curl pad and leg developer stations on the bench are detachable to maximize your space during workouts. 
Built-in Storage Space for your Training Accessories 
With so much included, the SM-7553 provides storage space so you don’t develop clutter. There are weight plate storage slots for your plates, two barbell storage posts, and storage hooks for some of your included accessories.

description: OPPSDECOR Smith machine is a versatile strength training equipment that allows you to perform a wide range of exercises in a safe and controlled manner. aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
UNLOCK YOUR GYM'S FULL POTENTIAL 
The go-to choice of countless home gym-goers worldwide, THEFITGUY extension straps are the ultimate accessory for adding new exercises and grip variations to your routine, compatible with gym handles, cable machines, pull-up bars, and more 
SUPERIOR RANGE OF MOTION 
Our innovative straps design lets you move farther. The extended range of motion activate muscles in new ways through deeper stretches and harder contractions. With these straps, you will finally feel your delts, lats, and other muscles like never before 
NEW GRIPS FOR MAXIMUM POWER 
Our straps allow natural rotating grip positions that conform to your body's specific mechanics. This enables full power transfer and premium comfort. Unlock your true strength potential through an optimized mind-muscle connection 
UNLOCK NEW FRONTIERS OF TRICEPS DEVELOPMENT 
Add new exercises and discover new possibilities as triceps straps. Available in 17.7" and 27.5" lengths, they enhance your range of movements, enabling limitless potential in triceps development 
UNRIVALED ADJUSTABILITY FOR TAILORED WORKOUTS 
Each strap can be easily adjusted to 5 lengths from 11" to 33.8" (excluding metal snap hooks lengths), providing maximum versatility. The 1.97" wide nylon strap and 2.67" wide D-ring ensure durable, secure attachment. We recommend measuring your gym setup to ensure best fit 
FORGED FOR THE HARDEST WORKERS 
Crafted with the upmost attention to detail and using top-quality materials, these straps are built to withstand rigorous workouts and frequent use. We take pride in delivering a product that meets the highest standards of quality and durability 
So what is so special about these straps? 
As passionate fitness enthusiasts ourselves, we designed these straps based on real-world experience. We truly believe we came up with the ultimate multifunctional straps that will take your home gym into the next level (as they took ours...) 
How can I be sure that the straps will fit my gym setup? 
We recommend measuring your gym setup and comparing it with the strap’s 5 adjustable length options and dimensions (1.97" wide strap and 2.67" wide D-rings) to ensure a secure and effective fit 
Is this thefitguy's original design? 
Yes. At thefitguy, we lead - not follow. We take pride in designing original products and hard to bring the best quality and the highest standards. When you choose our straps, you support original thinkers that keep it real 
I need only one strap - do you offer a single strap as well? 
Absolutely! go ahead and check out our products, we even have some bundles that you might be interested in 
What's in the package? 
In the package are 2 multifunctional straps and 4 metal snap hooks
